    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that's just it... why would i want to try again? that person who was capable, who was worth something, is gone for good. it feels so much more honest to just admit it's over. it's like trying to live as a ghost of your former self. it's exhausting and it doesn't feel like living anymore. it just feels like waiting for the end.",
